Scroll of Darkness
increase the user damage,spell amp and stats, when activating the item it will empower the next spell or basic attack

Active item use Dark Strike coldown 40 mana cost 10% of max mana
the next spell will deal 75% increase damage and for the next basic attack it will deal pure damage instead and will crit for 135% of
normal damage.

all stats 8-30
damage 5-40
spell amp 2%-20%


Scroll of Death
activate to deal high damage base on the missing hp of the enemy also increase spell amp, intelligence and mana

active item use Decay
deal 30 base damage magical to a enemy and for every 1% of health missing increase the base damage of Scroll of death by 15%
to cast the spell you will need to kill at least 30 unit, after getting that amount needed the spell will be ready for use, mana cost 50%
of current mana

spell amp 5%-35%
inteillgence 5-35
mana 50-350


Moon Shard
increase the user attack speed limit, attack speed and agility, also give some movement speed and attack speed to near ally, this effect
will have double its value for the user.

Passive item use
increase allys movement speed by 10% and attack speed by 30, double on user.

attack speed limit bonus 100
attack speed 45-90
agility 20-35

Dark Reef Water
increase the user Primary stats and health but lose health every seconds and can be use to deal all the health lost into damage for a
single target

Passive item use Black Water
the user will lose 3% health per second, cannot lose health when below 65% health

Active item use coldown 90 mana cost 20% of max mana
deal damage by the health taken away by Dark Reef Water into magic damage, cap damage is 35% of the user max health

Primary stat increase by 19-32
health 10%-25%

Medieval Artillery
this item is only useable for Davion, others will have this item muted, increase health with strenght but reduce movespeed of Davion.
Davion can also Use the item to call in a ROMAN CATAPULT

active item use ROMAN CATAPULT Coldown 125 no mana csot
Davion place a ROMAN CATAPULT to the target location 450 cast range, the Catapult will have 50% of the user health and deal 67-130 plus
65% of Davion primary Attribute and having 3.25 base attack time with 1250 attack range. the Catapult will also do splash damage in a 425
radius dealing 35% of its damage to others, it can also use the ability FLAMING BOULDER that deal 250 damage plus 50% of Davion Attributes
in pure damage, the radius is 625 and the cast range is 1250 cooldown of 11 second. The Catapult last 25 second.

health 650-1100
strenght 20-65
reduce movespeed 150 FLAT

Icy Hammer
the user attacks and physical spell will frosts enemys slowing their movespeed and attack speed also dealing damage everyseconds as well
and can stack 14 times on a single enemy. useing this item will deal damage base on how much stack they have. also increase damage and
strenght with agility but reduce attack speed

Passive item use Frost Mallet
every basic attack or physical spell will add 1 stack of Frost Mallet dealing 3 physical damage per stack and slowing attack speed by
4 and move speed by 1% for each stacks. stacks will last 2.7 seconds and deal the damage every 0.9 second

Active item use Frosting Blast coldown 54 mana cost 12% of max mana
deal 24 physical damage per stack of Frost Mallet on the target and every 7 stacks will deal 1% of the target max health in bonus
damage and at 14 stacks, the user will spellvamp for 45% of the damage dealt with Frosting Blast and will Freeze the target for 3.5
seconds making them stuns and increasing all Physical damage Source by 65% for the stun duration.

damage 29-55
strenght 15-40
agility 14-22
reduce attack speed 45
BAT 2.35


Radiant Core




Night Crest
Increase Healing Amp, Inteillgence, Agility and Spellamp, can also buff friendly allys giving them bonus healing amp and spellamp
and also increasing their Mana regeneration, can be use on enemys to debuff them reducing their magical damage output, healing Source
and reducing their mana regeneration as well, also gain a aura that buff allys and debuff enemys



